Robots! Everywhere! This is an alternate universe to the Daedalous we know! (And hate!) It has two GMs, but everyone has power! There is room for more people, so you're free to join! (Current Arc: 3 - The Cure and Aleliae)


Aleliae Research:
Each body has a d4-2 for parts if exploded, and a d4 if not exploded.
What each part is would be a d100.
1-35 = Scrap Alelianite x3
36-40 = Alelianite
41-50 = Storm Gun Fragment
51-55 = Storm Gun Battery
56-60 = Storm Bullet x12
61-65 = Personal Plasma Shield (PPS)
66-70 = PPS Battery
71 = AI Chip Fragment A
72 = AI Chip Fragment B
73 = AI Chip Fragment C
74 = AI Chip Fragment D
75 = AI Chip Fragment E
76-80 = Radar Chip
81-85 = Radio Chip
86-95 = Scrap Alelianite x2
96-99 = Minor Research Breakthrough!
100 = Major Research Breakthrough!

Each part has a quality:
(d10)+(Modifier)
1-3 = Bad
4-6 = Decent
7-9 = Good
10-12 = Great
13-15 = Excellent
16-18 = Perfect
(Some research/kills with certain weapons add a modifier to the quality)

Reasearch Breakthroughs are the most important part. They unlock new things to research, then later build.

Each research has a quality minimum, meaning that only things that quality or above can be used to build that item, unlock that item, and research that item. A Major Research with the quality good could not be unlocked with James's Bad Major Research Breakthrough. Just as, if it requires 12 Scrap Alelianite, all of that would have to be good quality or better.

Each research is Major, or Minor. Minor Research is unlocked with minor research breakthrough, and major research is unlocked with major research breakthroughs. Each research requires the previous one on the tree to be completed.

Each research has certain skills required to research it, a goal, and the dice to roll for gain.

James is the only person who can go through the research breakthroughs. (And knows what to unlock next, ect.)

Currently working on: =

Aleliae Cutting - Major Research - Bad

  • Can be worked on by: James, Techicians, Inventors, Scientists (-3 Modfifer)
  • Spends d3* working on it. Gains d8 per attempt.
  • Requires 80. (Left: 74) Also requires 8 Scrap Aleliae or 2 Aleliae. (We have 1, and 0)
  • Unlocks more reasearch.

Completed: =

Aleliae Metals - Minor Research - Bad

  • Finished (by James)
    • Unlocked more research.

*(Rock Paper Scissors. R = 1, P = 2, S = 3)

1 Decent Scrap Alelianite
1 PPS Battery
1 Storm Gun Fragment
